These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 8

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-1::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: photography, baking, filmmaking, puzzles
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: badminton, cycling, ice-hockey, cricket
1. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is between the person who's sport is ice-hockey and the person who's sport is cycling##2
2. the person who's hobby is puzzles is on the left or right of the person who's sport is ice-hockey##3
3. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is not to the left of the person who's sport is ice-hockey##8
4. the person who's sport is cycling is not the person who's hobby is filmmaking##6
5. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is photography##5
6. the person who's hobby is photography is on the right of the person who's sport is badminton##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1     |    2    |    3    |   4    |
| Hobby   | puzzles  | photography | filmmaking | baking  |
| Sport   | badminton | ice-hockey   | cricket  | cycling |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-2::.
There 4 different types of food: kiwi, asparagus, cherry, lemon
The people have 4 different jobs:  architect, software-developer, bartender, freelancer
1. the freelancer is not to the left of the freelancer##8
2. the person eating kiwi is somewhere to the right of the person eating lemon##5
3. the person eating kiwi is the software-developer##1
4. the person eating lemon is between the person eating kiwi and the person eating asparagus##2
5. the person eating asparagus is somewhere between the person eating cherry and the architect##7
6. the bartender is somewhere to the left of the person eating asparagus##5
7. the architect is not to the left of the architect##8

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1      |        2        |    3     |     4      |
| Food   | cherry | asparagus          | lemon | kiwi     |
| Job    | bartender      | freelancer | architect | software-developer |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-3::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  freelancer, pilot, chef, social-worker
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: time-travel, horror, western, disaster
1. the person watching time-travel movies is not to the left of the chef##8
2. the person watching horror movies is on the far left##1
3. the pilot is on the right of the freelancer##1
4. the pilot is in an even position##4
5. the social-worker is on the far left or far right##3
6. the freelancer is somewhere to the left of the person watching disaster movies##5
7. the social-worker is the person watching western movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |     3     |     4     |
| Job           | freelancer | pilot | chef     | social-worker |
| Movie-Genre   | horror    | disaster   | time-travel | western    |

