.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-4::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: soul, country, jazz, house
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: ice-hockey, handball, cricket, climbing
1. the person who's sport is handball is on the left of the person who's sport is climbing##1
2. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is not to the left of the person who's sport is handball##8
3. the person who's sport is cricket is on the right of the fan of country##1
4. the fan of house is not to the right of the person who's sport is cricket##8
5. the fan of soul is the person who's sport is ice-hockey##1
6. the fan of soul is on the right of the person who's sport is cricket##1
7. the fan of jazz is somewhere to the left of the fan of house##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |       2       |   3    |    4     |
| Music-Genre   | jazz   | country         | house   | soul    |
| Sport         | handball | climbing | cricket | ice-hockey |

