.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-5::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: martial-arts, drama, musical, sports
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: skiing, weightlifting, surfing, baseball
1. the person watching sports movies is somewhere between the person watching martial-arts movies and the person watching drama movies##7
2. the person watching musical movies is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is surfing##5
3. the person watching sports movies is somewhere between the person watching musical movies and the person watching martial-arts movies##7
4. the person watching musical movies is not to the left of the person who's sport is baseball##8
5. the person who's sport is baseball is somewhere between the person watching drama movies and the person who's sport is weightlifting##7
6. the person who's sport is weightlifting is somewhere to the right of the person watching sports movies##5
7. the person who's sport is weightlifting is not to the left of the person watching martial-arts movies##8
8. the person who's sport is weightlifting is on the left or right of the person watching sports movies##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |     3      |    4    |
| Movie-Genre   | drama   | musical | sports | martial-arts    |
| Sport         | skiing | baseball   | surfing   | weightlifting |

