The people prefer 4 different types of sport: parkour, skiing, biathlon, swimming
1. the person who's sport is skiing is not to the left of the person drinking coffee##8
2. the person who's sport is swimming is somewhere between the person drinking fanta and the person who's sport is biathlon##7
3. the person who's sport is biathlon is somewhere to the right of the person who's sport is parkour##5
4. the person who's sport is swimming is not to the left of the person who's sport is parkour##8
5. the person who's sport is swimming is not to the left of the person drinking coffee##8
6. the person drinking juice is on the left or right of the person drinking mirinda##3
7. the person who's sport is parkour is on the left of the person who's sport is biathlon##1
8. the person drinking juice is on the left of the person drinking fanta##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |     1     |   2    |      3      |    4    |
| Beverage   | coffee      | mirinda | juice | fanta   |
| Sport      | parkour | biathlon | swimming  | skiing |

