.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-9::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: salsa, electronic, disco, soul
The people use 4 different means of transport: skateboard, airplane, helicopter, jet-ski
1. the fan of salsa is between the fan of soul and the person driving the skateboard##2
2. the person driving the jet-ski is on the far left##1
3. the person driving the jet-ski is on the left or right of the fan of salsa##3
4. the fan of electronic is somewhere to the right of the person driving the skateboard##5
5. the person driving the airplane is the person driving the airplane##1
6. the fan of disco is not the person driving the helicopter##6
7. the fan of soul is not to the right of the fan of disco##8
8. the person driving the skateboard is not to the left of the person driving the airplane##8

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |     2     |   3   |    4    |
| Music-Genre   | soul   | salsa | disco | electronic |
| Transport     | jet-ski | airplane       | skateboard  | helicopter    |

