.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-12::.
There 4 different types of food: artichoke, peas, cherry, grapefruit
The people have 4 different hobbies: fishing, traveling, rock-climbing, woodworking
1. the person eating cherry is not to the right of the person who's hobby is woodworking##8
2. the person who's hobby is fishing is not to the right of the person eating peas##8
3. the person who's hobby is traveling is somewhere to the right of the person eating grapefruit##5
4. the person who's hobby is fishing is on the far left or far right##3
5. the person eating cherry is between the person who's hobby is woodworking and the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##2
6. the person eating peas is on the far left##1
7. the person eating cherry is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is woodworking##3

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |     2     |     3      |    4    |
| Food    | peas        | grapefruit | cherry      | artichoke    |
| Hobby   | fishing | rock-climbing   | traveling | woodworking |

