.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-13::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, coffee, 7up, lemonade
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: surfing, cricket, baseball, basketball
1. the person who's sport is basketball is not to the right of the person who's sport is surfing##8
2. the person who's sport is basketball is not to the right of the person drinking almond-milk##8
3. the person who's sport is cricket is on the left of the person drinking coffee##1
4. the person drinking almond-milk is on the far left or far right##3
5. the person drinking lemonade is on the far left or far right##3
6. the person who's sport is surfing is somewhere between the person who's sport is baseball and the person drinking coffee##7
7. the person who's sport is surfing is on the left or right of the person drinking coffee##3
8. the person drinking lemonade is on the left or right of the person drinking coffee##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |       2       |    3     |     4      |
| Beverage   | lemonade | coffee         | 7up    | almond-milk       |
| Sport      | cricket | basketball | surfing | baseball |

