 3. the person eating apricot is the person watching drama movies##1
 4. the person watching drama movies is not to the right of the person watching comedy movies##8
 5. the person watching documentary movies is on the right of the person eating pumpkin##1
 6. the person watching comedy movies is somewhere to the right of the person eating onion##5
 7. the person watching comedy movies is on the far left or far right##3
 8. the person eating apricot is not to the right of the person watching drama movies##8
 9. the person watching comedy movies is not to the left of the person eating apricot##8
10. the person eating pumpkin is not to the left of the person watching disaster movies##8

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |     3      |    4     |
| Food          | pumpkin    | onion | apricot | lime |
| Movie-Genre   | disaster | documentary  | drama     | comedy    |

