The people have 4 different hobbies: chess, cooking, writing, singing
1. the person eating eggplant is the person who's hobby is chess##1
2. the person eating eggplant is not to the left of the person who's hobby is cooking##8
3. the person who's hobby is cooking is the person who's hobby is cooking##1
4. the person who's hobby is singing is the person eating strawberry##1
5. the person eating strawberry is on the left of the person eating lettuce##1
6. the person eating lettuce is between the person who's hobby is cooking and the person eating strawberry##2
7. the person eating eggplant is in an even position##4

