.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-19::.
4 different pets are kept: mouse, guinea-pig, hedgehog, bird
The people use 4 different means of transport: snowmobile, roller, van, train
1. the owner of the bird is not the person driving the van##6
2. the person driving the van is not to the right of the owner of the hedgehog##8
3. the owner of the guinea-pig is somewhere between the owner of the hedgehog and the owner of the bird##7
4. the person driving the roller is somewhere to the right of the owner of the mouse##5
5. the person driving the roller is somewhere to the left of the person driving the train##5
6. the person driving the snowmobile is not to the right of the person driving the roller##8
7. the owner of the guinea-pig is not to the left of the person driving the train##8

.:: Answer ::.
|             |  1   |   2   |   3   |    4    |
| Pet         | mouse  | bird | guinea-pig  | hedgehog  |
| Transport   | snowmobile | roller   | train | van |

