.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-20::.
4 different pets are kept: rat, rabbit, snake, cat
The people use 4 different means of transport: ship, train, taxi, airplane
1. the person driving the train is not the owner of the rat##6
2. the person driving the taxi is on the right of the person driving the airplane##1
3. the owner of the cat is not to the left of the person driving the airplane##8
4. the owner of the snake is the person driving the ship##1
5. the owner of the cat is somewhere between the person driving the train and the person driving the ship##7
6. the owner of the cat is on the left of the owner of the rat##1
7. the person driving the taxi is between the person driving the airplane and the owner of the snake##2

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1    |    2     |     3      |    4    |
| Pet         | rabbit    | cat | rat | snake |
| Transport   | train | airplane      | taxi     | ship     |

 